on","id":301200,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"可是每一战都这么辛苦，@有多少条命都不够用啊……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}],"textRight":"哈哈……@[chara:100300:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:100300:cheek_0][chara:100300:motion_300][chara:100300:lipSynch_1]你说得对……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"志伸晶","textLeft":"但是巡的解说真是越听越上瘾啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}],"textLeft":"内容简洁又帅气，@听了之后让人大受鼓舞。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}],"textRight":"没错！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}],"textRight":"我听了之后也觉得充满干劲，@感觉自己无人能敌！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"枇枇木巡","textLeft":"啊……"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_11061.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101001,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":101001}],"nameCenter":"桃子","textCenter":"虽说战斗过程惊险……","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":101001}],"textCenter":"但是多亏了巡的解说，@我也有了不少干劲。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101001,"motion":200}],"textCenter":"最后还获得了戏剧性的胜利，@感觉真的很过瘾。"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21181.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":304200}],"textLeft":"桃子之前也对我说了同样的话……","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}],"textRight":"哦？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}],"textRight":"啊，我知道巡的能力了！"},{"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"到、到底是什么呢？！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}],"textRight":"那就是不论敌我，你都能鼓舞他人！"},{"chara":[{"id":100300}],"